Package edu.uiowa.cs.warp

Class GraphVizVisualization

java.lang.Object
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.Visualization
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.GraphVizVisualization
All Implemented Interfaces:
Visualizable
public class GraphVizVisualization extends Visualization
Builds a visualization of the sensor network as a directed graph. Each flow is represented as a set of directed edges in the sensor network. The .gv file is a GraphViz formated file that can be used with the GraphViz tools. The display graph is created with GraphStream.
Version:
2.0 Fall 2025
Author:
sgoddard
